{"tags":[{"name":"并查集","permalink":"http://lzy-foenix.github.io/tags/并查集/","url":"\\async\\tags\\并查集.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"图论","permalink":"http://lzy-foenix.github.io/categories/图论/","url":"\\async\\categories\\图论.json","count":19}],"url":"\\async\\posts\\2015\\03\\18\\BZOJ-1202[HNOI2005]狡猾的商人.json","date":1426634903000,"path":{"year":2015,"month":3,"day":18,"name":"BZOJ-1202[HNOI2005]狡猾的商人"},"title":"BZOJ-1202[HNOI2005]狡猾的商人","permalink":"http://lzy-foenix.github.io/2015/03/18/BZOJ-1202[HNOI2005]狡猾的商人/","content":"<hr>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"题解：\"><a href=\"#题解：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题解：\"></a>题解：</h3><p>大家都说这是水题，蒟蒻我就跪倒了，权值并查集神马的还是第一次听说.当我们询问一段区间的时候,既要考虑前面的影响,又要考虑对后面的影响,那么我们是要把这两个影响分开的,用并查集的话,就相当于一开始知道了[1,3]和[6,7],我们又知道了[4,5],这时候就可以进行合并了，这就是并查集。<br>对于一个集合内的元素，我们用sum[i]表示第i天到第fa[i]天的金钱差。如果查询的l和r在同一个集合内，就直接利用前缀和求差分，并与给出的val进行比较，不在一个集合内，就相当于这l，r之间有不确定的，那么就是“一切皆有可能”，所以我们只要合并就好了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"代码：\"><a href=\"#代码：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码：\"></a>代码：</h3><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div><div class=\"line\">5</div><div class=\"line\">6</div><div class=\"line\">7</div><div class=\"line\">8</div><div class=\"line\">9</div><div class=\"line\">10</div><div class=\"line\">11</div><div class=\"line\">12</div><div class=\"line\">13</div><div class=\"line\">14</div><div class=\"line\">15</div><div class=\"line\">16</div><div class=\"line\">17</div><div class=\"line\">18</div><div class=\"line\">19</div><div class=\"line\">20</div><div class=\"line\">21</div><div class=\"line\">22</div><div class=\"line\">23</div><div class=\"line\">24</div><div class=\"line\">25</div><div class=\"line\">26</div><div class=\"line\">27</div><div class=\"line\">28</div><div class=\"line\">29</div><div class=\"line\">30</div><div class=\"line\">31</div><div class=\"line\">32</div><div class=\"line\">33</div><div class=\"line\">34</div><div class=\"line\">35</div><div class=\"line\">36</div><div class=\"line\">37</div><div class=\"line\">38</div><div class=\"line\">39</div><div class=\"line\">40</div><div class=\"line\">41</div><div class=\"line\">42</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;cstdio&gt;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;cstring&gt;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"built_in\">std</span>;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> MAXN = <span class=\"number\">105</span>;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> W,N,M,f[MAXN],sum[MAXN],s,t,a;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">bool</span> flag = <span class=\"literal\">false</span>;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">inline</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">find</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(f[x]==x)<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> x;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> tmp=find(f[x]);</div><div class=\"line\">\tsum[x]+=sum[f[x]];</div><div class=\"line\">\tf[x]=tmp;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> f[x];</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">Work</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> s, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> t, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a)</span></span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> r1 = find(s), r2 = find(t);</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(r1 != r2)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\tf[r1] = r2;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\tsum[r1] = sum[t] - sum[s] - a;</div><div class=\"line\">\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(sum[t] - sum[s] != a)flag = <span class=\"literal\">true</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\tfreopen(<span class=\"string\">\"trader.in\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"r\"</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">stdin</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\tfreopen(<span class=\"string\">\"trader.out\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"w\"</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">stdout</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%d\"</span>, &amp;W);</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(W --)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"built_in\">memset</span>(sum, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">sizeof</span>(sum));</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%d%d\"</span>, &amp;N, &amp;M);</div><div class=\"line\">\t\tflag = <span class=\"literal\">false</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt;= N; i++)f[i] = i;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= M; i++)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%d%d%d\"</span>, &amp;s, &amp;t, &amp;a);</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t\tWork(s - <span class=\"number\">1</span>, t, a);</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(flag)<span class=\"built_in\">puts</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"false\"</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"built_in\">puts</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"true\"</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">\tfclose(<span class=\"built_in\">stdin</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\tfclose(<span class=\"built_in\">stdout</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>```</p>\n"}